<plot>A "Ham &amp; Hattie" cartoon which means two different cartoons splitting the seven minutes of running time. "Picnics are Fun" finds Hattie taking her two dolls for a picnic in the 'Country"---the roof of her apartment building where the trees, flowers and greenery grow only in her fertile imagination; the second offering, "Dino's Serenade", has Ham &amp; His World Players doing a sketch about a strolling musician, the girl he loves and the villain who steals her away.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?431980</url></doc>
